**** Price Reduction****

This spacious 4 bedroom, 2 and half bathroom sits on 1.44 acres in the Skyline Valley subdivision. This two story home offers little over 2300 sqft of space, high ceilings create an open and airy atmosphere adding to the overall grandeur of the home.  The primary bedroom is nicely situated on the first floor and the secondary bedrooms are all on the second floor; along with 2 dining and 2 living areas with a wood burning fireplace.
